container.content:
global
  #nbproc 4
  #daemon
  maxconn 2048
  log 127.0.0.1:64000 local0
  log 127.0.0.1:64000 local1 notice
container.name: global

container.content:
listen admin
  bind *:8088
  stats enable
  stats uri /haproxy?stats
container.name: mon

container.content:
listen srv1
  bind 192.168.51.15:64000
  server srv10 127.0.0.1:222 check
container.name: srv1
